meta.about: We are a Chinese restaurant serving traditional Shanghainese cuisine.  Started in 2018, our first shop in Tokwawan was closed in July 2021.  We are moving to the China Hong Kong City in Tsim Sha Tsui, and we plan to resume business in late Nov 2021.
